org.apache.cactus.server
Interface ImplicitObjects

All Known Subinterfaces:
WebImplicitObjects
public interface ImplicitObjects

Tagging interface for implicit objects. Implicit objects are objects that are instanciated by the containers and that need to be made visible to your test case classes.
